window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ordinary citizens are committing heinous acts of violence: a babysitter, a UPS driver, a college professor. Why are these seemingly normal New Yorkers committing such crimes? </b></p> <p>Homicide Detective Iris Williams and her partner, Detective Annette, are assigned to a case so baffling that it will leave them dumbfounded. In the meantime, a storm - more powerful than Hurricane Sandy - is headed toward the East Coast. Will Detectives Williams and Toni be able to unravel the perplexing murders that plagued the city, or will the perpetrator disappear with the storm?</p>"; 
